    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bars or shops where food and beverages are served, and often other provisions may be purchased, particularly such establishments located on a military base, school, factory, or other facility where many people of a particular group congregate.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000046693/Merriam-Webster's Collegiate Dictionary [online] (1997-2002)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cafés of winkels waar men voedsel en dranken serveert en vaak ook andere levensmiddelen kunnen worden gekocht, met name in militaire bases, scholen, fabrieken of andere gebouwen waarin een groot aantal mensen van een bepaalde groep bijeenkomt.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>供應食物與飲料的酒吧或商店，通常也可購買其他糧食，尤指位於軍事基地、學校、工廠或其他特定群體聚集之設施的機構。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Eine Bar oder ein Geschäft, in dem Essen und Getränke serviert werden. Häufig werden dort auch andere Vorräte verkauft, besonders in Einrichtungen wie Militärbasen, Schulen, Fabriken oder andere Anlagen, in denen viele Menschen einer bestimmten Gruppe zusammenkommen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
